==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lactonic
<hw>Lac*ton"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Lactone</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or
derived from, a lactone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lactonic</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Lactonic
<hw>Lac*ton"ic</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Lactose</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or designating, an acid obtained
by the oxidation of milk sugar (<xex>lactose</xex>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lactoprotein</ent>⟦br⟧
